From dcc7239dfd3ec9c6a9bcc909c9d72e6ee67776f7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: fi3 <email@email.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 01:07:48 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] ADD visual terminal selection yanks for focused panes

Terminal users need Vim-like selection across the chat and agent list panes without leaving the Work Leaf UI. The UI state tracks character, line, and block selections over rendered rows and emits OSC 52 clipboard copies for yanks while the harness covers the modal behavior.
